data.title: UCD Current Students
data.text:
Updated 09 July 2024

To access Online Registration, log into SISWeb using the Log in with UCD Connect button. Then click on My Registration.

Check out the Registration How-To Guides and Videos for help with what to do.

Keep an eye on the Google Calendar below for more dates.
